[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "馬戲團與龍族　前篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "很久很久以前，一隻年幼的龍族，與一名少年相遇了。他們都最喜歡快樂的事物了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「今天來做什麼快樂的事吧！」這句話成為了他們的暗號。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你追我跑、捉迷藏、對大人們惡作劇……有的時候也會想一些新的遊戲。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "某天，少年所住的村子裡，搭起了一座色彩鮮豔的帳篷。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「這一定是很快樂的東西！」於是他們與馬戲團相遇了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "空中飛人、拋短劍、馴獸師以及小丑的雜技……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "在眼前一幕幕上演著耀眼不已的演出，他們看得非常入迷。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「馬戲團好開心喔！」「我們也來試看看吧！」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "小小的馴龍師便在這個瞬間誕生了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "接著他們向村子裡的大人們展示自己所想出來的技藝──雖然規模很小，但對少年和幼龍來說，已經是十分優秀的馬戲團表演了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖微小，卻快樂的馬戲團。但是，所謂的表演，終究會有落幕的時刻。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但此時的他們，對如此理所當然的命運也還無法理解。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 210043011, "title": "馬戲團與龍族　前篇"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "馬戲團與龍族　後篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "被馬戲團深深打動的少年與幼龍，將只屬於他們的馬戲團表演展示給村人們看。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "百花齊放的春天，陽光耀眼的夏天，遍地楓紅的秋天，銀雪覆蓋的冬天。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "他們從不厭倦地日復一日地表演著，但閉幕時刻卻突然地造訪了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「今天也來玩馬戲團吧！」「抱歉，我還有家裡的事要幫忙。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「今天要來玩馬戲團了吧！」「抱歉，我得照顧孩子才行。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「今天也不能玩馬戲團嗎？」「抱歉啊……　我已經，不能像小時候一樣　自由地活動身體了。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "孩子總有一天會長大成人。不管是龍族還是人類都一樣。但是，彼此成為大人的時間，卻殘酷地有著遙遠的差距。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "即使看著身旁，卻再也沒有友好搭檔的身影。曾一起練習技藝的搭檔，成為了大人、老去，最終離開了人世。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為了填補寂寞，龍族決定將村子與少年以及曾經快樂的馬戲團全都忘掉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但即使如此，心中已深根蒂固的思念卻不斷湧出。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「想與人類一起做快樂的事情。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "龍族祈願著，希望有一天那與人類共度的快樂時光能再次到來。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是，無論度過了多少寒暑，龍族仍舊感到無聊至極，並深深感到了孤獨。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「快樂的事情，　可能已經不會再發生了吧。」龍族像是放棄一般，嘆了口氣。就在那時──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「我說你啊，一臉陰沉的樣子呢。　如果你願意的話，　要不要一起去看馬戲團表演？」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "迴盪在耳中的，是那令他懷念的詞彙。映照在眼中的，是那令他懷念的帳篷。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "龍族眼中閃爍著光芒，他對天空發出了欣喜的咆吼。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "在那之後，帶著龍族的少女和她的馬戲團，將令熱鬧的氣氛充滿在巷弄之間。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而聽說少女與龍族，今天也向許多的人展現著快樂的演出。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "如果你懷疑是真是假，就去那色彩鮮豔的帳篷之中親眼確認真偽吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你聽，應該很快就可以聽見開演的鈴聲了──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 210043012, "title": "馬戲團與龍族　後篇"}]